"Robust Password Generator" - This tool allows users to create secure and customized passwords effortlessly.

Tailored Complexity: Users have the control to set the length and complexity of their passwords. Whether it's a strong, complex passphrase 
or a shorter, secure combination, this generator caters to individual preferences.

Interactive Generation: Not satisfied with the first result? Click the submit button to generate multiple password options until you find 
the one that meets your security criteria. Your security, your way.

User-Friendly Interface: The application features an intuitive design for seamless navigation. It's designed to be accessible to users of all 
technical backgrounds, ensuring a smooth and efficient password generation process.

GUI: Python tkinter
Other Modules used: Random and string modules
Programming concepts implemented - Functions, Loops, Conditional statements
